## 8. KEY HOOKS USED

### useDbSearch (lines 17, 361-365 in snippet_manager_view)
Full-text search with fallback to fuzzy matching. Returns `{ results, invalidate }` where:
- `results`: FTS search results or null if no FTS available
- `invalidate()`: Clear cache when data changes

### useNavigation
Provides breadcrumbs for hierarchy navigation

### useAlert
For confirmation dialogs. API:
```typescript
const { alertState, confirmAlert, dismiss } = useAlert();
confirmAlert({
  title: string,
  message: string,
  icon?: ReactNode,
  primaryAction: { label, style, onAction },
  dismissAction: { label, style, onAction },
});
```

### useHUD
Toast notifications:
```typescript
const { items, show } = useHUD();
show({ icon: <Icon />, title: 'Action completed' });
```

### useKeyboardShortcut
